        ]
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "to walk in all his ways; prescribed and directed to by him, every path of duty, whether moral, ceremonial, or judicial: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "and to love him, and to serve the Lord thy God with all thy heart, and with all thy soul; for that is the best service which springs from love, and love constrains unto, and which is hearty and sincere, as that is, and is performed in the best manner such are capable of. ",
        "children": [
